---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Skills from '../molecules/Skills.astro';
import aboutMe from '../../assets/img/about-me-image.svg';
---

<div>
	<Skills />

	<div class='flex items-center justify-center sm:justify-start gap-3 mb-[30px] sm:px-5 mt-[50px]'>
		<div class='w-[80px] h-[80px] bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-700 to-slate-900 rounded-full overflow-auto'>
			<Image
				src={aboutMe}
				alt='about me'
				class='w-full h-full'
				loading='lazy'
				draggable='false'
			/>
		</div>
		<div class='leading-[30px]'>
			<h2 class='text-[#DDF4FB] text-[26px] sm:text-[35px] font-bold'>Hi I'm Cristian</h2>
			<h3 class='text-[#43CFF4] text-[18px] sm:text-[24px] font-bold'>front-end web developer</h3>
		</div>
	</div>
	<p class='text-[#DDF4FB] text-[18px] sm:text-[22px] max-w-[738px] px-5'>
		I am passionate about technology in general, I have had a great approach to web development when I discovered how amazing this world is, so I
		decided to become a front-end web developer, in this way I have been able to learn and implement modern web technologies, let's do amazing
		things together.
	</p>
</div>
